      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REIN ME IN (1) had the drop on the lead from the squeeze box before taking over turning, drawing clear to score (21.85) at this track in a Maiden over 390m. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Looks to have an edge on most of these. FORTUNE HEARTS (3) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 3rd on April 28 over 457m at this track behind Typhoon Pablo beaten 5.5 lengths (25.85) in a Grade 6. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Well-placed to take this out. FLAMING VALORA (2) scored two back then was always well back and could manage only a 9 length 8th at Q Straight (19.99). Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Should be about the mark. GOLDSTAR HUNTER (6) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
